      • listeners

        private java.util.List<GraphicElementClipboardEntryListener> listeners
        List of currently registered listeners.

      • listenersToAdd

        private java.util.List<GraphicElementClipboardEntryListener> listenersToAdd
        As we cannot add listeners while iterating over them to fire an event, this keeps tabs on listeners added in other listeners' on* methods, so they can be added when the iteration is finished.

      • listenersToRemove

        private java.util.List<GraphicElementClipboardEntryListener> listenersToRemove
        As we cannot remove listeners while iterating over them to fire an event, this keeps tabs on listeners removed in other listeners' on* methods, so they can be removed when the iteration is finished.

      • inCriticalSection

        private boolean inCriticalSection
        Tracks whether we're inside a critical section, i.e. currently iterating over listeners as a result of an event firing.

      • pastedCount

        private int pastedCount
        Number of times this entry has been pasted. Used to cascade elements when pasting.

    • Method Detail

      • enterCriticalSection

        private void enterCriticalSection()
        Enters a critical section. Called when iterating over listeners in order to notify them of events starts.

      • exitCriticalSection

        private void exitCriticalSection()
        Exits a critical section. Called when iterating over listeners in order to notify them of events ends. All listener register and listener unregister requests made during the critical section are applied here.
